@startuml AppleCore
    [*] --> Green

    state "Táo Xanh" as Green
    state "Táo Chín" as Ripe
    state "Táo Thối" as Rotten
    state "Ăn Táo" as Eaten
    state "Thùng rác" as Trash

    Green --> Ripe: Chính dần
    Ripe --> Eaten: Ăn
    Ripe --> Rotten: Bỏ quá lâu

    Rotten --> Trash: Vứt vào

    Eaten --> [*]
    Trash --> [*]